<title>HONG KONG: Merrill Lynch sets warrants on red chip basket.</title>
<headline>Merrill Lynch sets warrants on red chip basket.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-04-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Merrill Lynch International &amp; Co C.V. said on Friday it has launched 730 million American style call warrants on a basket of four red chip stocks.</p>
<p>Each basket comprises of:</p>
<p> Shanghai Industrial Holdings Ltd	   0.1  shrs</p>
<p> Shum Yip Investment Ltd			0.15 shrs</p>
<p> China Everbright-IHD pacific Ltd	   0.1  shrs</p>
<p> China Merchant Hai Hong Holdings Ltd     0.1  shrs</p>
<p>Ten warrant control one basket.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE	 HK$6.588	  PREMIUM	 20.29 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE	  HK$0.175	  GEARING	 3.96x</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	   24.APR.98	 MIN EXER LOT  10,000</p>
<p> REFERENCE SPOT     HK$6.935	  PAYMENT DATE  14.MAY.97</p>
<p> LISTING		HONG KONG	 LISTING DATE  15.MAY.97</p>
<p> NOTE		   CASH OR PHYSICAL SETTLEMENT</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2843 6370</p>
